{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-js","path":"/operations/continuous-deployment/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d5db2c20-fd12-5a14-bb0a-cf9aa85aa904","html":"<h1 id=\"argocd-custom-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#argocd-custom-image\" aria-label=\"argocd custom image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ArgoCD Custom Image</h1>\n<p>This repo contains the Operate-First ArgoCD custom Image. The image is used by the Operate-First ArgoCD repo-server deployment. Below is a list of the tools packed into this image. See the <code class=\"language-text\">Dockerfile</code> for more info.</p>\n<h3 id=\"tools-included-in-the-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools-included-in-the-image\" aria-label=\"tools included in the image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools included in the Image</h3>\n<p>We use the following tools with corresponding versions.</p>\n<p>ArgoCD: 2.0.1</p>\n<p>KSOPs: 2.5.5</p>\n<p>Kustomize: 4.1.1</p>\n<p>SOPS: 3.7.1</p>\n<p>Helm: 3.4.1</p>\n<p>Helm-Secrets: 3.4.1</p>\n<p>The KSOPS and Kustomize versions refer to the ones provisioned with ArgoCD.</p>\n<p>Kustomize versions can be adjusted manually using <a href=\"https://argoproj.github.io/argo-cd/user-guide/kustomize/#custom-kustomize-versions\">customized versions</a>.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/continuous-deployment/blob/master/README.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null,"extraClasses":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"d5db2c20-fd12-5a14-bb0a-cf9aa85aa904"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","3000541721","3606484676","533861647"]}